sentences.english: By means of the method, a full-scale test pile in Zhenjiang Port has been analysed.

sentences.english: Right now, Hockaday's prototypes put out only a few milli- watts of power.

sentences.english: Metal-wheeled chariots are the prototype of the tanks of modern warfare.

sentences.english: This was done to avoid cluttering the prototype with too much detail.

sentences.english: At the end of this stage, the course should be prototyped.

sentences.english: The result of a demiurge's act of creation is a Progenitor, the prototype Promethean of a Lineage.

sentences.english: It is easy and quick to prototype interactive widgets and animated transitions.

sentences.english: Another one is around the development of prototyping.

sentences.english: Also, prototype cars have been built on this principle.
